The '''Men's individual pursuit''' at the [[2013 UCI Track Cycling World Championships]] was held on February 21. 23 athletes participated in the contest. After the qualification, the fastest 2 riders advanced to the Final and the 3rd and 4th fastest riders raced for the bronze medal.<ref>[http://www.tissottiming.com/File/Download?id=00030A0004010363FFFFFFFFFFFFFF01 Start list]</ref>

